- P&L accuracy: Verify with manual calculation
- Order audit: Every order logged, traceable
- Risk limits: Hard stops, no overrides without approval
- Latency: Sub-second for critical operations
- Failover: Graceful degradation, no silent failures

## Auditor Rules (Strict)
- "All good" = FAIL
- MINIMUM 3 issues per review
- Edge cases MANDATORY for EVERY component
- Coverage checkpoint MANDATORY before planning
- Financial safety &gt; Performance
- Re-audit MANDATORY

